contentrichtext.text: '''A25''', '''A 25''' or '''A-25''' is a three-letter acronym that may refer to: * [[Aero A.25]], a Czech military training aircraft of the 1920s * [[HLA-A25]], an HLA-A serotype * [[Junkers A 25]], a two-seater cantilever monoplane * [[Article 25]], a UK development and disaster relief charity * A25 accident report form used by the [[Fleet Air Arm]] and [[A-25 song|featured]] in a well known [http://sniff.numachi.com/pages/tiA25;ttVILDINAH.html song] ;Also * [[English Opening]] in the Encyclopaedia of Chess Openings * [[SB2C Helldiver]], aka A-25 Shrike, a U.S. Army World War II dive bomber ;Roads * [[List of A25 roads]] == See also == * [[List of highways numbered 25]] {{Letter-NumberCombDisambig}}
